{
  "id": "69d07e22b718d5ea3eef0bcf",
  "title": "想起の習慣",
  "created": 1775271489,
  "updated": 1775271944,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69d07e22b718d5ea3eef0bcf",
      "text": "想起の習慣",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271489,
      "updated": 1775271489
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f140000000000ef4553",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271700,
      "updated": 1775271703
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f9f0000000000ef4556",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271839,
      "updated": 1775271839
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f180000000000ef4554",
      "text": " 準備なしにいつでもできる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271704,
      "updated": 1775271837
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f950000000000ef4555",
      "text": "  スマホを出して行うことだと、スマホを取り出して、アンロックして、アプリを立ち上げるまでに時間がかかる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271829,
      "updated": 1775271876
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07fc30000000000ef4557",
      "text": "   歩行者信号が変わってしまう",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271876,
      "updated": 1775271886
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07fd40000000000ef4558",
      "text": " ながら作業できる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271893,
      "updated": 1775271897
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07fd80000000000ef4559",
      "text": "  皿洗いやお風呂掃除をしながらできる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271897,
      "updated": 1775271923
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ff40000000000ef455a",
      "text": "  歩きながらできる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271925,
      "updated": 1775271927
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e400000000000ef4542",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271489,
      "updated": 1775271489
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e400000000000ef4543",
      "text": "[行動遡行]と似てる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271489,
      "updated": 1775271492
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e440000000000ef4545",
      "text": " [行動遡行]とは、1つ前の行動を思い出す、それを繰り返してどんどん時間を遡っていく作業",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271492,
      "updated": 1775271609
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ebc0000000000ef454d",
      "text": " 例えば、いまお風呂にいるとしたら",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271612,
      "updated": 1775271630
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ecd0000000000ef454e",
      "text": "  お風呂に入る前に脱衣所で服を脱いだ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271629,
      "updated": 1775271645
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07edc0000000000ef454f",
      "text": "  その前にトイレに行った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271645,
      "updated": 1775271650
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ee20000000000ef4550",
      "text": "  その前に髪をとかした",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271650,
      "updated": 1775271662
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07ee80000000000ef4551",
      "text": "  その前に部屋から移動して脱衣所に服を持って行った",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271656,
      "updated": 1775271687
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07f080000000000ef4552",
      "text": "  その前に……",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271688,
      "updated": 1775271691
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e640000000000ef4548",
      "text": " 知った場所",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271525,
      "updated": 1775271526
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e660000000000ef454a",
      "text": "  どこだっけ[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271526,
      "updated": 1775271528
    },
    {
      "id": "69d07e9b0000000000ef454c",
      "text": "  心の調子を良くするものとしてWeb記事で紹介されていた気がする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1775271579,
      "updated": 1775271596
    }
  ]
}